    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Strategically positioned architecture at the service of national defence. The structures serve the functional purpose of manning weaponry and maintaining military communication and transport routes.The shape of these buildings changes according to the military technology of a period.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000303/ANET</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000110115/Anet, working group AAT</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Strategisch geplaatste architectuur ten dienste van landsverdediging. De bouwwerken hebben als functioneel doel om wapentuig te bemannen en het onderhouden van militaire communicatie- en transportroutes. De vorm van deze bouwwerken verandert naargelang de militaire technologie van een periode.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000303/ANET</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000110115/Anet, working group AAT</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Arquitetura estrategicamente posicionada ao serviço da defesa nacional. As estruturas têm a finalidade funcional de guarnecer armamento e manter rotas de comunicação e transporte militar. A forma desses edifícios muda de acordo com a tecnologia militar de uma época.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Portuguese</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
